            <div xml:lang="en" type="translation" xml:space="preserve">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/>Elias and Aphous
                    <lb n="2"/>chiefs of the [...]
                    <lb n="3"/>the 5th Indiction [...]
                    <lb n="4"/>of Isidorus, chief of the Jews-
                    <lb n="5"/>, greetings. We have received from you
                    <lb n="6"/>the full portion due to you
                    <lb n="7"/>for the 5th Indiction
                    <lb n="8"/>and we have no complaint
                    <lb n="9"/>against you.
                    <space quantity="1" unit="line"/>
                    <lb n="10"/>Aphous and Elias
                    <lb n="11"/>we have sent. Phaophi 8.
